00:41:00,962 --> 00:41:04,214
No. They just left.

703
00:41:04,214 --> 00:41:06,258
But my sister
should be back soon.

704
00:41:06,258 --> 00:41:09,260
Do you mind if I ask you
a few questions?

705
00:41:09,260 --> 00:41:11,221
