874
00:50:59,792 --> 00:51:03,629
accidental manslaughter
will hurt your chances.

875
00:51:03,629 --> 00:51:04,880
God.

876
00:51:11,135 --> 00:51:13,096
When did you find out?

877
00:51:15,597 --> 00:51:17,683
We got the call this morning.

878
00:51:17,683 --> 00:51:21,144
