sometimes.

886
00:51:39,077 --> 00:51:43,290
Yeah. Every now and then,
I get a little blue.

887
00:51:43,290 --> 00:51:46,333
What on God's earth did Charles
have to be depressed about?

888
00:51:46,333 --> 00:51:50,588
Charles is gone.
