891
00:52:00,930 --> 00:52:02,599
A note?

892
00:52:04,058 --> 00:52:09,314
"My darkness descends deeper
than I knew it could."

893
00:52:10,564 --> 00:52:15,151
"Enveloped in the blackness,
I search for some light."

894
00:52:18,112 --> 00:52:23,201
"Maybe now...
Maybe this time."

895
00:52:26,286 --> 00:52:29,290
What a beautiful note!

896
00:52:29,290 --> 00:52:31,708
Did you really like the note?

897
00:52:34,127 --> 00:52:36,712
Of course we like the note.

898
00:52:36,712 --> 00:52:40,132
What kind of
