at his coming-home party.

902
00:52:50,517 --> 00:52:53,811
Maybe he didn't
want to be here.

903
00:52:55,854 --> 00:52:59,733
I have never seen you
this talkative before!

904
00:52:59,733 --> 00:53:01,735
Children, I'm afraid
there are still...

905
00:53:01,735 --> 00:53:05,530
certain details to discuss.

906
00:53:05,530 --> 00:53:07,448
The funeral...

907
00:53:12,119 --> 00:53:15,747
Before we get into that,
I was thinking about...

908
00:53:17,582 --> 00:53:19,417
The organ donation centre...

909
00:53:19,417 --> 00:53:21,253
You know what I was thinking?

910
00:53:21,253 --> 00:53:23,630
I was thinking that Charles
would have liked it...

911
00:53:23,630 --> 00:53:26,465
if we donated
his organs to science.

912
00:53:26,465 --> 00:53:30,719
Iris, that's
an excellent idea!

913
00:53:30,719 --> 00:53:32,638
Harry.

914
00:53:33,639 --> 00:53:34,722
Harry?

915
00:53:36,057 --> 00:53:38,060
Do you really think
