916
00:53:38,060 --> 00:53:40,144
Yes.

917
00:53:40,144 --> 00:53:43,481
Yes, I think it's appropriate.

918
00:53:43,481 --> 00:53:47,150
Otherwise, I wouldn't
have suggested it.

919
00:53:47,150 --> 00:53:51,154
Yes. My Charles
would have liked that.

920
00:53:51,154 --> 00:53:53,240
Thank you, Iris.

921
00:54:16,093 --> 00:54:18,138
