929
00:54:35,027 --> 00:54:37,488
Then try being happy for me
for once, OK?

930
00:54:40,657 --> 00:54:41,867
OK.

931
00:54:45,536 --> 00:54:48,414
So, tell me about him.

932
00:54:48,414 --> 00:54:51,751
He's not like the men
I usually date.

933
00:54:51,751 --> 00:54:53,585
He has a job?

934
00:54:53,585 --> 00:54:56,129
Yeah. And we haven't
known each other that long...

935
00:54:56,129 --> 00:54:58,632
but we talked all night
on the phone.

936
00:54:58,632 --> 00:55:01,176
