he loves fish.

937
00:55:01,176 --> 00:55:04,053
Not only that,
but he has a tank.

938
00:55:04,053 --> 00:55:06,890
It's small, but he says
he wants to get a bigger one.

939
00:55:06,890 --> 00:55:09,558
