to his fish.

940
00:55:09,558 --> 00:55:11,560
It's more
than just fish, though.

941
00:55:11,560 --> 00:55:13,728
We're getting
to know each other.

942
00:55:13,728 --> 00:55:16,148
He told me about
his two old girlfriends.

943
00:55:16,148 --> 00:55:18,274
I'm telling him
about my past relationships.

944
00:55:19,734 --> 00:55:22,612
The weirdest thing is,
I owe it all to you.

945
00:55:22,612 --> 00:55:24,404
What do you mean?

946
00:55:24,404 --> 00:55:26,908
I met him at your place
last night...

947
00:55:26,908 --> 00:55:28,909
and I'm nuts about him.

948
00:55:28,909 --> 00:55:30,827
Last night?

949
00:55:30,827 --> 00:55:32,913
