investigating a crank call.

951
00:55:36,542 --> 00:55:37,751
What?

952
00:55:37,751 --> 00:55:40,461
Does he work
for the telephone company?

953
00:55:40,461 --> 00:55:43,713
Nope. He's a cop.

954
00:55:45,215 --> 00:55:46,759
Cop? A policeman?

955
00:55:46,759 --> 00:55:49,803
There was a policeman
in my house last night?

956
00:55:49,803 --> 00:55:54,390
Yep. And I am going to be
at his house tonight.

957
00:55:54,390 --> 00:55:55,767
Why didn't you tell me this?

958
00:55:55,767 --> 00:55:57,602
I forgot.

959
00:55:57,602 --> 00:55:59,019
Does Harry know?

960
00:55:59,019 --> 00:56:01,021
No. I was going to call
you guys and tell you...

961
00:56:01,021 --> 00:56:03,064
only Wilbur called...
that's his name, Wilbur...

962
00:56:03,064 --> 00:56:06,110
and we talked all night,
so I thought I'd tell you today.

963
00:56:06,110 --> 00:56:07,735
This is just like you!

964
00:56:07,735 --> 00:56:09,654
It's no big deal.

965
00:56:09,654 --> 00:56:12,240
Only he still
needs to talk to you.

966
00:56:12,240 --> 00:56:15,451
Me? Why?

967
00:56:15,451 --> 00:56:17,245
There was
this crank call made...

968
00:56:17,245 --> 00:56:19,913
and he said they traced it
back to your house.

969
00:56:19,913 --> 00:56:22,124
What do you mean
by a crank call?

970
00:56:22,124 --> 00:56:24,458
A 911 call.

971
00:56:24,458 --> 00:56:26,962
Oh, lord.

972
00:56:26,962 --> 00:56:28,921
Don't worry. I told him
it was a mistake.

973
00:56:28,921 --> 00:56:30,631
Did he believe you?

974
00:56:30,631 --> 00:56:32,799
Of course!
Why wouldn't he?

975
00:56:32,799 --> 00:56:36,095
