was going to happen.

976
00:56:36,095 --> 00:56:38,930
Wilbur needs to talk to you
about this crank call...

977
00:56:38,930 --> 00:56:40,932
on account of he's up
for police chief...

978
00:56:40,932 --> 00:56:43,434
and he wants to cover
all his bases.

979
00:56:43,434 --> 00:56:47,479
Only I don't want you to say
anything bad about me, OK?

980
00:56:47,479 --> 00:56:51,150
I really like this guy.
All right?

981
00:56:51,150 --> 00:56:52,734
OK!

982
00:56:52,734 --> 00:56:54,486
