too powerful for him.

1026
00:59:29,083 --> 00:59:31,585
He had himself a heart attack!

1027
00:59:31,585 --> 00:59:33,087
While you were...

1028
00:59:33,087 --> 00:59:34,130
After!

1029
00:59:34,130 --> 00:59:37,466
I think it was after.
I hope it was after.

1030
00:59:47,099 --> 00:59:48,601
Howie, is that you?

1031
00:59:48,601 --> 00:59:49,602
No.

1032
00:59:49,602 --> 00:59:53,105
