1365
01:14:11,211 --> 01:14:13,587
Of course you'd lose him,
you... slut!

1366
01:14:13,587 --> 01:14:15,047
Shut up, Iris!
Just shut up!

1367
01:14:16,173 --> 01:14:18,509
All of you! This is between
