Like my birthday?

1397
01:16:01,142 --> 01:16:03,395
Do you think I haven't
had opportunities?

1398
01:16:03,395 --> 01:16:05,230
Because, boy, have I had...

1399
01:16:05,230 --> 01:16:06,981
