1400
01:16:06,981 --> 01:16:09,317
They're everywhere.
The way they look at me...

1401
01:16:09,317 --> 01:16:12,069
in my waiting room,
outside the E.R.

1402
01:16:12,069 --> 01:16:15,572
Two years ago, at the colon
convention in Atlanta...

1403
01:16:15,572 --> 01:16:19,326
