the wrong thing to say.

1417
01:16:57,610 --> 01:17:00,612
I was desperate
to talk to Harry...

1418
01:17:00,612 --> 01:17:04,616
to tell him the truth about
what I did and why I did it...

1419
01:17:04,616 --> 01:17:07,619
