1422
01:17:11,539 --> 01:17:13,458
I couldn't stop
thinking about Harry.

1423
01:17:13,458 --> 01:17:16,627
I didn't know where he was.

1424
01:17:16,627 --> 01:17:19,422
Harry hadn't just
disappeared from my life...

1425
