1456
01:18:38,118 --> 01:18:41,245
when she moved her
10-gallon tank into his house.

1457
01:18:43,455 --> 01:18:46,625
As for me, I couldn't control
my feelings anymore.

1458
01:18:46,625 --> 01:18:49,502
So I tried to contain
them on paper...

1459
01:18:56,134 --> 01:18:59,511
After I figured out
how to use a typewriter.

1460
01:19:07,102 --> 01:19:10,354
Six months passed before I
realized I hadn't lost my mind.

1461
01:19:10,354 --> 01:19:13,650
